1
00:00:11,083 --> 00:00:12,707
Your people prepared for hundreds of years,

2
00:00:13,375 --> 00:00:15,249
and this is the only secret tunnel you dug?

3
00:00:16,083 --> 00:00:18,249
This is beneath the Cathedral of the Church of Light!

4
00:00:18,583 --> 00:00:19,749
Just sneaking in here,

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,124
and figuring out how to haul the dirt out

6
00:00:21,125 --> 00:00:22,125
without being detected

7
00:00:22,625 --> 00:00:23,749
was already a miracle.

8
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:34,957
Careful!

9
00:00:35,333 --> 00:00:36,457
Blood-sucking bats!

10
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:38,207
They've built a nest here.

11
00:00:40,250 --> 00:00:41,416
This baby is here!

12
00:00:41,708 --> 00:00:43,541
Make way, everyone!

13
00:01:10,917 --> 00:01:12,624
This is the Barrier of Light I told you about.

14
00:01:13,250 --> 00:01:14,332
We Necromancers

15
00:01:14,750 --> 00:01:16,249
are restrained by this pure power.

16
00:01:16,917 --> 00:01:18,082
There is no breaking through.

17
00:01:18,625 --> 00:01:20,041
So that's why you sought me out.

18
00:01:32,792 --> 00:01:33,792
It worked.

19
00:01:34,792 --> 00:01:35,792
Or maybe not.

20
00:01:36,792 --> 00:01:37,792
Could it be...

21
00:01:37,917 --> 00:01:39,166
you didn't use enough blood?

22
00:01:40,083 --> 00:01:41,083
How about...

23
00:01:47,417 --> 00:01:49,832
My blood shares the same attribute
as the barrier.

24
00:01:50,542 --> 00:01:52,041
Contacting it only causes fusion.

25
00:01:52,917 --> 00:01:54,707
Even if I drained all the blood
from my body,

26
00:01:55,167 --> 00:01:56,207
it probably wouldn't work.

27
00:01:58,667 --> 00:02:00,666
Is there really no way at all?

28
00:02:02,625 --> 00:02:03,625
If gentle doesn't work,

29
00:02:03,792 --> 00:02:04,792
use force.

30
00:02:05,042 --> 00:02:06,499
If we use opposing attributes,

31
00:02:07,083 --> 00:02:08,166
it might be effective.

32
00:02:26,458 --> 00:02:27,458
It worked!

33
00:02:28,083 --> 00:02:29,874
With my current power, I can't break
it open.

34
00:02:30,417 --> 00:02:31,999
Plus, this barrier self-repairs.

35
00:02:33,417 --> 00:02:34,417
Brother Leon,

36
00:02:34,792 --> 00:02:35,792
this favor is troubling me.

37
00:02:36,125 --> 00:02:37,125
It went inside.

38
00:02:42,958 --> 00:02:43,958
Little Dragon,

39
00:02:44,292 --> 00:02:45,292
how did you get in?

40
00:02:47,083 --> 00:02:48,416
I'm not quite sure myself.

41
00:02:48,958 --> 00:02:52,041
It felt like the power of the Great
Priest of Light was helping me.

42
00:02:53,208 --> 00:02:55,041
Because it absorbed the God Relic?

43
00:02:55,375 --> 00:02:56,791
Little Dragon, try again.

44
00:02:57,125 --> 00:02:58,125
Try again.

45
00:02:58,292 --> 00:03:00,041
Maybe you can break the seal.

46
00:03:00,250 --> 00:03:01,250
Alright.

47
00:03:01,333 --> 00:03:03,249
Since Little Leon is asking me,

48
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:08,957
Excellent!

49
00:03:09,250 --> 00:03:10,250
It really went in.

50
00:03:10,458 --> 00:03:11,832
Sanders the Sage is saved!

51
00:03:14,333 --> 00:03:15,416
Seems safe inside.

52
00:03:15,875 --> 00:03:16,875
Let's go in too.

53
00:03:57,250 --> 00:03:58,250
Brother Chen,

54
00:03:58,542 --> 00:03:59,542
looking for books?

55
00:04:00,333 --> 00:04:02,082
I'm investigating an ancient secret.

56
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:04,707
Books written in the common tongue
of the past millennium are useless.

57
00:04:05,250 --> 00:04:06,916
First, gather all the ancient language
books.

58
00:04:09,917 --> 00:04:11,624
This is the den of the Church of Light.

59
00:04:11,958 --> 00:04:13,291
Looks like on this wanted list,

60
00:04:13,333 --> 00:04:14,457
neither of us can escape.

61
00:04:16,833 --> 00:04:17,833
What is there to fear?

62
00:04:18,083 --> 00:04:19,249
Heavy debts make light of danger.

63
00:04:25,750 --> 00:04:26,750
Alright, alright.

64
00:04:27,667 --> 00:04:29,499
I have some knowledge of Western
ancient script.

65
00:04:30,042 --> 00:04:31,874
Most books here are religious texts.

66
00:04:32,375 --> 00:04:33,707
Take out the books from your ring,

67
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,000
I'll help filter them.

68
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:38,250
Works for me.

69
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,000
Chen Nan,

70
00:05:17,042 --> 00:05:18,791
I found a glowing book.

71
00:05:19,333 --> 00:05:20,624
It has a barrier on it.

72
00:05:21,042 --> 00:05:22,749
That must be a treasure of the
Church of Light.

73
00:05:25,417 --> 00:05:25,999
Little Dragon,

74
00:05:26,083 --> 00:05:27,083
we're counting on you.

75
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:28,250
Alrighty!

76
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:50,166
This barrier feels suffocating.

77
00:05:50,792 --> 00:05:52,624
Like walking through a swamp.

78
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,082
Everything feels sticky.

79
00:05:55,958 --> 00:05:57,832
I'll reward you with a red wine bath
tonight.

80
00:06:00,042 --> 00:06:01,416
Yay!

81
00:06:02,375 --> 00:06:04,291
Then I'll swim a few more laps.

82
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:16,875
Brother Leon,

83
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,000
check these few first.

84
00:06:30,958 --> 00:06:32,207
Yu Xin's handwriting.

85
00:06:33,083 --> 00:06:34,083
She's been here.

86
00:06:36,292 --> 00:06:37,957
The Du family is ungrateful.

87
00:06:38,833 --> 00:06:40,041
They betrayed the Chen family.

88
00:06:41,083 --> 00:06:42,916
Forcing Yu Xin into marriage.

89
00:06:44,875 --> 00:06:45,749
"I will not marry."

90
00:07:02,958 --> 00:07:04,124
"Rain sparse, wind sudden..."

91
00:07:10,583 --> 00:07:12,624
After a life-and-death battle,

92
00:07:13,250 --> 00:07:14,541
Yu Xin slew the Du family Martial God,

93
00:07:15,250 --> 00:07:16,666
but was gravely injured herself.

94
00:07:18,625 --> 00:07:20,249
Hesitating on whether to reincarnate.

95
00:07:21,375 --> 00:07:22,957
She ultimately decided to travel
west,

96
00:07:23,542 --> 00:07:25,124
seeking aid from the Goddess of Life.

97
00:07:27,125 --> 00:07:28,874
Yu Xin became the Corpse Spirit King...

98
00:07:29,500 --> 00:07:31,957
meaning she didn't find a way to
continue her life.

99
00:07:32,417 --> 00:07:33,749
And finally perished.

100
00:07:34,917 --> 00:07:36,832
Her death was actually caused by
the Du family.

101
00:07:37,292 --> 00:07:39,916
These wicked slaves who benefited
from my Chen family...

102
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,166
Du family!

103
00:07:42,875 --> 00:07:44,499
I will grow stronger.

104
00:07:45,125 --> 00:07:47,791
And wipe out every single one of you.

105
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:50,374
Brother Chen,

106
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:51,750
Brother Chen, restrain yourself!

107
00:07:53,167 --> 00:07:54,499
Don't lash out!

108
00:07:54,917 --> 00:07:55,624
If this place breaks,

109
00:07:55,917 --> 00:07:56,917
we're all finished.

110
00:08:08,042 --> 00:08:09,042
Brother Chen, you...

111
00:08:11,458 --> 00:08:12,458
I'm fine.

112
00:08:17,542 --> 00:08:18,957
Chen Nan, give me a hand.

113
00:08:20,542 --> 00:08:21,582
We made quite a commotion.

114
00:08:22,208 --> 00:08:23,291
This isn't a good place to linger.

115
00:08:38,167 --> 00:08:39,167
Wrap it up.

116
00:08:41,125 --> 00:08:42,125
Let's go.

117
00:08:42,458 --> 00:08:44,207
To save your necromancer sage.

118
00:08:50,208 --> 00:08:51,499
The seal on this floor...

119
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:54,250
it's stronger.

120
00:09:03,750 --> 00:09:04,832
What is this thing?

121
00:09:05,333 --> 00:09:06,832
I confess my crime...

122
00:09:09,708 --> 00:09:11,791
I have been imprisoned for a hundred
years.

123
00:09:12,667 --> 00:09:13,832
I confess...

124
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:17,207
I am a sinner.

125
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:19,374
The entire second layer of hell

126
00:09:19,542 --> 00:09:21,249
holds undead creatures.

127
00:09:22,333 --> 00:09:23,333
Corpse demons,

128
00:09:23,375 --> 00:09:24,375
wraiths,

129
00:09:24,542 --> 00:09:25,542
bone devils.

130
00:09:26,792 --> 00:09:29,124
The truly terrifying figures are
on the lower floors.

131
00:09:30,083 --> 00:09:32,249
The Church of Light is truly formidable.

132
00:09:33,083 --> 00:09:35,666
To suppress so many powerful beings
underground.

133
00:09:39,958 --> 00:09:40,999
Lord Sanders,

134
00:09:41,333 --> 00:09:42,333
where are you?

135
00:09:42,917 --> 00:09:43,999
Lord Sanders!

136
00:09:49,875 --> 00:09:52,749
Little Sanders, where are you?

137
00:09:53,333 --> 00:09:55,957
Your Leon is here to find you!

138
00:09:56,375 --> 00:09:57,457
Leon?

139
00:09:58,333 --> 00:09:59,457
Is that Leon?

140
00:10:01,042 --> 00:10:02,499
Is Leon here?

141
00:10:02,625 --> 00:10:03,625
Lord Sanders!

142
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:08,291
Your Sanders is actually a ball of
fire.

143
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,249
Undead all look like this.

144
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:12,249
Leon...

145
00:10:12,917 --> 00:10:14,374
I'm almost done for.

146
00:10:15,833 --> 00:10:17,999
Quickly break the seal!

147
00:10:37,542 --> 00:10:38,542
San—

148
00:10:42,250 --> 00:10:43,250
It's very weak.

149
00:10:43,875 --> 00:10:44,957
If I weren't holding it,

150
00:10:45,167 --> 00:10:47,666
it would probably be torn apart
passing through the barrier.

151
00:10:49,583 --> 00:10:50,583
Lord Sanders!

152
00:10:51,542 --> 00:10:52,542
After thousands of years,

153
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:54,000
I just knew

154
00:10:54,583 --> 00:10:56,999
that even the Pope of the Church
of Light couldn't destroy you.

155
00:10:58,125 --> 00:11:00,166
I never had that kind of strength.

156
00:11:00,667 --> 00:11:02,957
They merely spared my life.

157
00:11:04,125 --> 00:11:06,499
This old undead holds no resentment
after escaping.

158
00:11:06,708 --> 00:11:08,041
Nor does he threaten revenge.

159
00:11:08,833 --> 00:11:10,207
Truly worthy of the name "Sage."

160
00:11:11,667 --> 00:11:13,249
Someone's been rescued!

161
00:11:13,833 --> 00:11:15,082
Let me out!

162
00:11:15,583 --> 00:11:16,999
Save me too!

163
00:11:18,042 --> 00:11:19,042
Save us!

164
00:11:19,292 --> 00:11:20,541
Save us!

165
00:11:20,542 --> 00:11:21,542
Leave first.

166
00:11:21,708 --> 00:11:23,374
The commotion might attract guards.

167
00:11:23,875 --> 00:11:24,875
Go!

168
00:11:30,583 --> 00:11:34,499
To casually break a barrier formed
by Divine Light...

169
00:11:35,250 --> 00:11:36,541
that little dragon...

170
00:11:37,667 --> 00:11:38,791
Your Holiness, disaster!

171
00:11:39,792 --> 00:11:41,249
Someone invaded the second layer
of hell.

172
00:11:41,708 --> 00:11:43,249
And rescued a necromancer.

173
00:11:44,250 --> 00:11:45,791
I'll send people to stop them now!

174
00:11:47,125 --> 00:11:48,125
No.

175
00:11:48,417 --> 00:11:49,791
Let them go.

176
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:54,166
But Cardinal Malun must already know.

177
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,791
If you don't take action,

178
00:11:56,167 --> 00:11:57,167
Enough.

179
00:11:58,042 --> 00:11:59,999
No matter what actions Malun takes,

180
00:12:00,542 --> 00:12:01,957
you are not to interfere.

181
00:12:07,708 --> 00:12:09,457
Go to the first layer of hell.

182
00:12:10,083 --> 00:12:12,666
Return the books from this spatial
ring

183
00:12:12,917 --> 00:12:14,249
to their original places.

184
00:12:15,250 --> 00:12:16,250
Remember,

185
00:12:16,667 --> 00:12:18,707
you saw nothing.

186
00:12:20,958 --> 00:12:21,958
Yes.

187
00:12:28,083 --> 00:12:29,832
This den of the Great Priest of Light...

188
00:12:29,875 --> 00:12:31,916
turns out you can just waltz in
and out.

189
00:12:43,708 --> 00:12:44,999
Many thanks, Divine Dragon.

190
00:12:45,250 --> 00:12:48,041
And thanks to this unknown young
man for his aid.

191
00:12:48,542 --> 00:12:49,749
Congratulations on your freedom,
Great Sage.

192
00:12:51,542 --> 00:12:52,207
Brother Chen,

193
00:12:52,708 --> 00:12:54,666
I told Sanders about our agreement.

194
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:57,874
He promises to tell you the whereabouts
of the Great Dragon Blade.

195
00:12:59,167 --> 00:13:01,207
In my long life,

196
00:13:01,917 --> 00:13:03,624
I have indeed heard

197
00:13:04,125 --> 00:13:06,416
of that number one divine weapon
in the world.

198
00:13:06,958 --> 00:13:09,499
It is most likely lost

199
00:13:09,958 --> 00:13:14,041
in the depths of the ancient elven
tribe's primeval forest.

200
00:13:15,042 --> 00:13:17,624
That is all I know.

201
00:13:18,875 --> 00:13:20,541
That Godfallen Land...

202
00:13:21,125 --> 00:13:22,457
It feels like destiny,

203
00:13:22,708 --> 00:13:24,916
some force is drawing me there.

204
00:13:26,042 --> 00:13:27,082
Thank you for the information,
senior.

205
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:29,750
Our cooperation is complete.

206
00:13:31,250 --> 00:13:32,250
Brother Chen,

207
00:13:32,417 --> 00:13:33,417
we part ways here.

208
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,207
When did the ring disappear?

209
00:13:47,875 --> 00:13:49,207
I didn't notice a thing.

210
00:13:52,833 --> 00:13:54,457
To hide it from both of us...

211
00:13:55,083 --> 00:13:58,499
that person likely used a lost art
of spatial magic.

212
00:13:59,250 --> 00:14:01,124
Possessing such terrifying ability,

213
00:14:01,667 --> 00:14:03,582
yet letting us leave with the rescue...

214
00:14:05,083 --> 00:14:07,332
Looks like the Church of Light isn't
so clean either.

215
00:14:08,292 --> 00:14:09,624
But regardless,

216
00:14:10,333 --> 00:14:11,333
Du family...

217
00:14:16,083 --> 00:14:17,082
Your Eminence,

218
00:14:17,667 --> 00:14:18,667
your guess was correct.

219
00:14:19,333 --> 00:14:21,541
The Dark Church has no intention
of sparing Chen Nan.

220
00:14:22,417 --> 00:14:23,499
In the coming days,

221
00:14:23,875 --> 00:14:25,457
they will make new moves.

222
00:14:27,042 --> 00:14:28,249
Continue.

223
00:14:28,833 --> 00:14:30,124
I also received news

224
00:14:30,500 --> 00:14:32,749
that members of the Eastern Supreme
Royal Family, the Du clan,

225
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,457
will arrive in Baidan tomorrow.

226
00:14:35,458 --> 00:14:36,624
Chen Nan has issued a challenge to
them.

227
00:14:36,625 --> 00:14:37,625
Chen Nan has issued a challenge.

228
00:14:39,333 --> 00:14:40,333
Oh?

229
00:14:41,292 --> 00:14:43,291
Then I'll add a little something.

230
00:14:44,333 --> 00:14:47,082
Take two men, disguise yourselves
as Dark Church members.

231
00:14:47,542 --> 00:14:50,332
Before the duel date, go assassinate
him.

232
00:14:50,875 --> 00:14:51,461
Yes.

233
00:14:52,375 --> 00:14:53,999
Pope...

234
00:14:54,583 --> 00:14:57,041
Although I don't know what you're
planning,

235
00:14:57,667 --> 00:14:59,832
since you let him go,

236
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:03,499
I will make sure he dies.

237
00:15:05,583 --> 00:15:10,416
[Eighteen Layers of Hell: A mysterious artifact containing eighteen worlds, each sealed with a powerful ancient being. The deeper you go, the stronger the enemy. Defeat them to advance— a prison, and a trial of strength.]

238
00:15:11,208 --> 00:15:13,332
You Du family truly court death.

239
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:15,041
I didn't come looking for you,

240
00:15:15,833 --> 00:15:17,791
yet you deliver yourselves to my door.

241
00:15:20,750 --> 00:15:22,541
The desert scenery is nice.

242
00:15:23,125 --> 00:15:24,874
Perfect place for your graves.

243
00:15:26,083 --> 00:15:27,416
All things return to the flow.

244
00:15:28,250 --> 00:15:29,666
Heaven-shaking, Earth-shattering!

245
00:15:32,208 --> 00:15:33,208
I say,

246
00:15:33,958 --> 00:15:34,958
you Du family...

247
00:15:35,125 --> 00:15:37,332
don't you have anything of your own?

248
00:15:37,356 --> 00:15:53,356
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

249
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,000
This aura...

250
00:15:55,125 --> 00:15:56,125
It's so strong.

251
00:16:11,458 --> 00:16:12,749
Du family dogs!

252
00:16:13,750 --> 00:16:14,750
Descendant of the Chen family!

253
00:16:15,250 --> 00:16:16,250
You seek death!

254
00:16:17,417 --> 00:16:19,332
You Du family truly court death.

255
00:16:19,958 --> 00:16:21,332
I didn't come looking for you,

256
00:16:22,833 --> 00:16:24,749
yet you deliver yourselves to my door.

257
00:16:26,833 --> 00:16:28,791
But to think killing a side branch
of the Du family

258
00:16:29,333 --> 00:16:30,707
would make you so arrogant.

259
00:16:31,625 --> 00:16:32,749
Wake up!

260
00:16:33,083 --> 00:16:34,957
The Chen family's era is long past.

261
00:16:35,375 --> 00:16:36,832
In this world now,

262
00:16:37,375 --> 00:16:38,957
my Du family calls the shots.

263
00:16:47,625 --> 00:16:50,207
Leeching off my Chen family's Profound
Arts to survive for ten thousand
years,

264
00:16:50,458 --> 00:16:52,457
and you dare claim to be masters?

265
00:16:53,125 --> 00:16:55,416
Nothing but rats who can't be put
on the stage.

266
00:16:55,708 --> 00:16:56,708
Impudent!

267
00:16:59,292 --> 00:17:00,292
True enough.

268
00:17:00,458 --> 00:17:01,832
The Chen family was once glorious.

269
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:03,916
But ten thousand years have passed,

270
00:17:04,833 --> 00:17:06,082
it has long since turned to dust.

271
00:17:21,417 --> 00:17:22,417
And your existence

272
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,874
should be erased from this world.

273
00:17:43,708 --> 00:17:45,541
The desert scenery is nice.

274
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,707
Perfect place for your graves.

275
00:17:48,250 --> 00:17:49,832
All things return to the flow.

276
00:17:50,167 --> 00:17:52,041
Heaven-shaking, Earth-shattering!

277
00:18:09,125 --> 00:18:10,957
Even after ten thousand years,

278
00:18:11,375 --> 00:18:12,791
as long as I live,

279
00:18:13,417 --> 00:18:14,624
you Du family

280
00:18:15,625 --> 00:18:18,207
will forever be servants of my Chen
family!

281
00:18:39,208 --> 00:18:40,416
Damn it!

282
00:19:07,375 --> 00:19:08,375
The rumors are true.

283
00:19:08,875 --> 00:19:10,582
Their Profound Arts stem from the
same root.

284
00:19:11,083 --> 00:19:12,083
Same root...

285
00:19:12,292 --> 00:19:13,582
I can already judge who is superior.

286
00:19:13,958 --> 00:19:15,499
Chen Nan clearly has the upper hand.

287
00:19:19,583 --> 00:19:20,583
Du Hong!

288
00:19:31,542 --> 00:19:32,832
Finger of Imprisonment!

289
00:19:44,917 --> 00:19:45,999
Hand of Annihilation!

290
00:20:02,125 --> 00:20:03,125
I say,

291
00:20:03,375 --> 00:20:04,499
you Du family...

292
00:20:04,833 --> 00:20:06,832
don't you have anything of your own?

293
00:20:15,042 --> 00:20:16,042
Ten thousand years have passed.

294
00:20:16,458 --> 00:20:19,207
Countless noble families and experts
have founded sects,

295
00:20:19,417 --> 00:20:20,624
creating their own lineages.

296
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,332
Yet your Du family

297
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,957
doesn't even have its own inherited
techniques.

298
00:20:25,167 --> 00:20:26,457
How pathetic.

299
00:20:26,542 --> 00:20:27,249
This is...

300
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:28,500
Demonic energy!

301
00:20:28,542 --> 00:20:29,542
The intel was real.

302
00:20:30,208 --> 00:20:31,332
He didn't cultivate the Lower Volume.

303
00:20:32,292 --> 00:20:33,292
But rather...

304
00:20:33,625 --> 00:20:34,625
reversed the Xuan Gong.

305
00:20:35,333 --> 00:20:36,333
Impossible.

306
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:37,832
How could the Xuan Gong be reversed?

307
00:20:38,667 --> 00:20:39,957
You lot could never achieve it.

308
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:43,374
Did that fool Du Yu not tell you?

309
00:20:43,917 --> 00:20:45,499
This Chen Family Xuan Gong

310
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,416
can only be reversed by me.

311
00:20:47,958 --> 00:20:49,416
These paths of Gods and Demons...

312
00:20:50,083 --> 00:20:52,457
I alone may tread upon them.

313
00:20:54,167 --> 00:20:55,707
Betraying the Chen family—

314
00:20:56,000 --> 00:20:57,249
that is disloyalty.

315
00:20:58,375 --> 00:20:59,749
Driving Yuxin to her death—

316
00:21:00,208 --> 00:21:01,457
that is inhumanity.

317
00:21:02,167 --> 00:21:04,291
Disloyal, inhumane, shameless wretches...

318
00:21:05,583 --> 00:21:06,749
deserve to die.

319
00:21:19,833 --> 00:21:20,833
What?

320
00:21:38,917 --> 00:21:39,917
You...

321
00:21:40,292 --> 00:21:42,499
You hid your true strength when killing Du Yu.

322
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:47,499
It seems your strength isn't lacking...

323
00:21:47,542 --> 00:21:49,249
but your wits are dull.

324
00:21:49,833 --> 00:21:52,082
You're only realizing that now?

325
00:21:55,083 --> 00:21:56,083
Madman.

326
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:57,458
The Elder was right.

327
00:21:57,583 --> 00:21:59,291
All you Chens are raving lunatics.

328
00:22:03,042 --> 00:22:04,042
Mad?

329
00:22:04,458 --> 00:22:06,832
Blood debts must be repaid in blood.

330
00:22:08,042 --> 00:22:09,291
To kill...

331
00:22:09,833 --> 00:22:12,124
one must accept the risk of being killed.

332
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:56,332
No...

333
00:23:16,333 --> 00:23:16,916
I...

334
00:23:17,083 --> 00:23:18,707
I am of the Du family.

335
00:23:18,833 --> 00:23:19,957
I know.

336
00:23:20,333 --> 00:23:21,457
The Elders said...

337
00:23:22,292 --> 00:23:26,582
we Du descendants are born rulers of this world.

338
00:23:27,042 --> 00:23:28,832
So why...

339
00:23:29,292 --> 00:23:31,332
did I have to die by your hand?

340
00:23:32,333 --> 00:23:34,791
When my father granted you the Xuan Gong,

341
00:23:35,042 --> 00:23:36,042
that was the cause.

342
00:23:36,500 --> 00:23:38,207
Today, I claim your lives...

343
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:39,707
that is the effect.

344
00:23:42,250 --> 00:23:43,916
Only thus can we call it...

345
00:23:44,083 --> 00:23:45,791
a settling of karma.

346
00:23:50,125 --> 00:23:51,125
Jin Bai.

347
00:23:51,833 --> 00:23:53,999
Who else wishes to step forward?

348
00:23:57,833 --> 00:23:58,332
Chen Nan.

349
00:23:58,375 --> 00:23:59,375
Watch out!

350
00:24:02,333 --> 00:24:04,332
The Dark Church's Twin Saint Dragon Knights.

351
00:24:04,417 --> 00:24:04,957
Talida...

352
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:05,707
and Andeni.

353
00:24:05,833 --> 00:24:07,457
We are here for revenge for our old friend.

354
00:24:08,417 --> 00:24:09,707
Where did these scoundrels crawl out from?

355
00:24:11,292 --> 00:24:13,707
They actually have the gall to attack a junior.

356
00:24:14,208 --> 00:24:15,416
Reaping the benefits...

357
00:24:15,833 --> 00:24:17,374
the Dark Church truly is shameless.

358
00:24:18,667 --> 00:24:21,041
I, Chen, am quite enjoying this slaughter.

359
00:24:21,083 --> 00:24:22,083
You two...

360
00:24:22,333 --> 00:24:24,041
care to test your mettle?

361
00:24:25,083 --> 00:24:26,291
You Eastern whelp...

362
00:24:26,792 --> 00:24:28,249
you know nothing of the world.

363
00:24:42,500 --> 00:24:43,082
That is...

364
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,500
the Divine Dragon.

365
00:24:45,583 --> 00:24:46,583
Return.

366
00:24:46,917 --> 00:24:47,957
This isn't a fight for you.

367
00:24:48,833 --> 00:24:50,291
Or you'll fall into slumber again.

368
00:24:51,292 --> 00:24:52,292
Relax.

369
00:24:52,583 --> 00:24:54,082
These two are nothing.

370
00:24:54,083 --> 00:24:55,249
They can't touch me.

371
00:24:55,625 --> 00:24:56,625
Mm.

372
00:24:58,333 --> 00:24:59,624
With the Divine Dragon present,

373
00:25:00,333 --> 00:25:02,041
our Saint Dragons won't stand a chance.

374
00:25:02,833 --> 00:25:03,833
No.

375
00:25:04,083 --> 00:25:05,707
The Divine Dragon seems uninterested in fighting.

376
00:25:06,208 --> 00:25:06,957
Now is our chance.

377
00:25:07,167 --> 00:25:08,167
Kill him!

378
00:25:24,833 --> 00:25:25,833
Chen Nan.

379
00:25:26,042 --> 00:25:27,541
His Dragon Tongue Magic is instant-cast.

380
00:25:28,083 --> 00:25:29,374
It will hold you back.

381
00:25:30,667 --> 00:25:33,832
This desert shall be your burial ground.

382
00:25:36,167 --> 00:25:37,541
Just you two?

383
00:25:37,917 --> 00:25:39,457
It is not enough.

384
00:25:39,958 --> 00:25:41,332
An attack of this level...

385
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,916
cannot break a Saint Dragon's defense.

386
00:26:05,583 --> 00:26:07,041
Young, yet so accomplished.

387
00:26:07,667 --> 00:26:08,707
What a pity.

388
00:26:23,000 --> 00:26:24,000
Seize this moment.

389
00:26:40,667 --> 00:26:41,416
Chen Nan.

390
00:26:41,667 --> 00:26:43,249
You are truly a peerless genius.

391
00:26:43,875 --> 00:26:45,166
Perhaps in another ten years,

392
00:26:45,667 --> 00:26:47,749
the entire Dark Church couldn't stop you.

393
00:26:51,625 --> 00:26:52,625
It is a shame...

394
00:26:53,292 --> 00:26:54,541
you have no time left.

395
00:26:55,500 --> 00:26:57,166
Pray to your gods...

396
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,791
for a quick death.

397
00:27:11,625 --> 00:27:13,207
Do you really think...

398
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:15,332
you have me cornered?

399
00:27:28,958 --> 00:27:30,832
I have seen enough...

400
00:27:31,292 --> 00:27:32,582
of your skills.

401
00:27:34,125 --> 00:27:35,582
Now...

402
00:27:36,250 --> 00:27:37,332
it is my turn.

403
00:28:04,542 --> 00:28:06,624
A Saint Dragon's defense is impregnable.

404
00:28:06,625 --> 00:28:07,625
How is this possible?

405
00:28:17,417 --> 00:28:18,417
Talida!

406
00:28:35,833 --> 00:28:36,916
Saint Dragon...

407
00:28:39,708 --> 00:28:41,624
is merely a toy in my hands.

408
00:29:02,083 --> 00:29:03,083
How...

409
00:29:03,333 --> 00:29:04,333
could this be?

410
00:29:14,625 --> 00:29:16,582
Such loyalty and devotion...

411
00:29:17,833 --> 00:29:19,999
I shall send you all on your way together.

412
00:29:43,333 --> 00:29:44,791
Consuming mountains and seas...

413
00:29:45,083 --> 00:29:46,124
power shattering a thousand weights.

414
00:29:47,125 --> 00:29:48,624
Truly terrifying.

415
00:30:04,375 --> 00:30:05,707
His strength is exhausted.

416
00:30:06,292 --> 00:30:07,292
The time has come.

417
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:12,500
Despicable!

418
00:30:12,583 --> 00:30:13,832
They're resorting to a tag-team battle.

419
00:30:14,458 --> 00:30:14,916
It's over...

420
00:30:15,375 --> 00:30:16,749
How many enemies does this guy have?

421
00:30:17,208 --> 00:30:18,832
Shameless cowards.

422
00:30:21,958 --> 00:30:22,499
Damn it.

423
00:30:22,958 --> 00:30:24,082
He deliberately lured us out.

424
00:30:28,792 --> 00:30:30,624
Those who came to die today...

425
00:30:31,208 --> 00:30:32,791
are truly numerous.

426
00:30:33,417 --> 00:30:35,457
Rise up.

427
00:30:36,812 --> 00:30:41,351
[God-Trapping Finger: An ancient sealing technique that binds even the strongest foes. It suppresses power and prevents escape— a single strike is enough to seal everything.]

428
00:30:42,763 --> 00:30:44,059
[Next Episode Preview]

429
00:30:44,083 --> 00:30:45,083
Tell me...

430
00:30:47,042 --> 00:30:49,832
have peerless masters become so cheap?

431
00:30:50,542 --> 00:30:53,416
Showing up one after another to die.

432
00:30:58,208 --> 00:30:59,791
You've finally revealed a flaw.

433
00:31:00,208 --> 00:31:01,457
The ultimate law...

434
00:31:01,833 --> 00:31:04,041
transcends all laws of this world.

435
00:31:04,833 --> 00:31:05,957
How does one transcend?

436
00:31:07,042 --> 00:31:08,457
By reforging heaven and earth.

437
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,124
And creating a new realm.

438
00:31:10,148 --> 00:31:42,548
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

